### Move category to a new parent
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/11/move?parentId=2

### Move category to root (no parent)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/11/move

### Move - circular reference (IllegalArgumentException)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/11/move?parentId=1

### Move - own parent (IllegalArgumentException)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/1/move?parentId=1